      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014it seriously looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-parked and sparkling clean. It drives like a total dream and is ready for your next big road trip. If you're looking for something that's basically flawless, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
