      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. At its heart lies the S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system that has been fully overhauled for peak volumetric efficiency. Power is routed through a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring surgical torque delivery. The chassis is structurally pristine, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain factory suspension kinematics. With its original paint depth preserved and a flawless interior, this vehicle offers a visceral, analog driving experience with zero mechanical compromise.",
